name: I am the places that i have been.
description:
The earth has marked me so deep that I have become it.
I've been traveling a long time to get here, so I have kept everything I found inside.
I never stopped walking and my heart is still growing up.
I´m every place i have been.
This land today it is in my skin.

Picture from Cafayate, Salta, Argentina.
Quebrada de las Conchas.

3000x2000 px
